//hermes commands can be executed by clicking the lifesaver icon on the top right corner of every application.
//It also serves as a live IT support.

//globally enabled commands
/refresh-[app_method] //refresh any page that has the method provided in app_method field. eg. /refresh-swi

//argus related commands
/do-argus-[stage]-[shipment] //dummy real-time stage update for argus stages are as follows [started,ready_qa,verified,loading,loaded,release,ship_completed] eg. /do-argus-ready_qa-WR01535889